\begin_layout Standard
Animal Shelter Manager is a computer package designed to ease the administrative
 burden of managing an animal shelter or sanctuary.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
It integrates well with existing paper-based systems, and offers a whole
 host of features, including:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Adoption history facilities, allowing full animal tracking
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Advanced media facilities for attaching photographs, documents, spreadsheets,
 videos and sounds.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Automatic insurance number generation for pet insurer agreements
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Full reporting facilities, including auditing, financials, statistics and
 graphs.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Complete double-entry book keeping system for account management.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Flexible custom reporting allows editing, saving, emailing, embedding in
 documents, direct uploading to the internet and conversion to many different
 word processor formats, as well as built in tools to generate your own
 reports.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Form creation facilities for instant generation of adoption paperwork, reservati
on cards etc.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Web site generation to allow a wider audience to see your animals, including
 integration to PetFinder.com and other major US adoption websites.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Lost and found database facilities with intelligent matching system
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Easy-maintenance database with low resource requirements for easy backing
 up using backup tapes, zip drives and CD writers.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Owner and donation management, including UK Gift Aid support, homechecking,
 banned owners, etc.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Sophisticated animal search facilities allowing staff to locate an animal
 within the shelter at a glance
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Low specification computers required for both server and clients with the
 option to use many different operating systems and platforms
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Extensible architecture allows for easy creation of third party plugins
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Bulk mail shotting and email facilities based on filtered criteria
\end_layout

