 colour, animals adopted to an owner with the surname black, etc.
 Results are sorted by relevance, so if the term appears in an animal's
 name or code, it will be at the top of the list.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
By clicking the Advanced button, you can go to a more sophisticated search
 screen that allows you to search by animal location and state, age, etc.
