\begin_layout Standard
A large part of the administrative duties you will need to perform with
 Animal Shelter Manager revolve around the 
\begin_inset Index idx
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
movement
\end_layout

\end_inset

movement and reservation
\begin_inset Index idx
status open

