Word will now prompt you through a three-step process, where you must either
 open an existing document or turn the current document into a mail merge
 document (you may choose from Form Letters, Address Labels etc.)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Step two prompts you to get the data source - simply find the csv file in
 your mailmerge directory and select it.
 Note that by default Word will not show the csv files in it's dialog -
 make sure you drop down the file type list and select 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

All Files (*.*)
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

